commit.message: Updated Cirrus css to fix weird margin positioning problem, removed Bootstrap
fixed json error, post recursion, duplicate subredditt viewing
Better mobile support, displays upvotes and comments, updated design
removed remaining gopherjs and renamed view.html
Fixed image sizing issues, mostly fixed grid layout issues, fixed CSS crash where it tried to register CSS folder multiple times
Added JsonQ lib and ability to fetch all links
Removed page.go because we do not need file input/output.
Added Page struct (object) with simple load and save functions.
